{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":786,"text":"I'm five years old, and I am very proud."},{"time":4781,"text":"My father has just built the best outhouse"},{"time":8340,"text":"in our little village in Ukraine."},{"time":10930,"text":"Inside, it's a smelly,\ngaping hole in the ground,"},{"time":14479,"text":"but outside, it's pearly white formica"},{"time":18485,"text":"and it literally gleams in the sun."},{"time":22113,"text":"This makes me feel so proud, so important,"},{"time":25670,"text":"that I appoint myself the leader\nof my little group of friends"},{"time":28710,"text":"and I devise missions for us."},{"time":31490,"text":"So we prowl from house to house"},{"time":33803,"text":"looking for flies captured in spider webs"},{"time":37170,"text":"and we set them free."},{"time":39557,"text":"Four years earlier, when I was one,"},{"time":41865,"text":"after the Chernobyl accident,"},{"time":43310,"text":"the rain came down black,"},{"time":45641,"text":"and my sister's hair fell out in clumps,"},{"time":47841,"text":"and I spent nine months in the hospital."},{"time":50398,"text":"There were no visitors allowed,"},{"time":51950,"text":"so my mother bribed a hospital worker."},{"time":55962,"text":"She acquired a nurse's uniform,"},{"time":58693,"text":"and she snuck in every night\nto sit by my side."},{"time":63038,"text":"Five years later,\nan unexpected silver lining."},{"time":66098,"text":"Thanks to Chernobyl,\nwe get asylum in the U.S."},{"time":70200,"text":"I am six years old, and I don't\ncry when we leave home"},{"time":74419,"text":"and we come to America,"},{"time":75470,"text":"because I expect it to be\na place filled with rare"},{"time":79218,"text":"and wonderful things\nlike bananas and chocolate"},{"time":83398,"text":"and Bazooka bubble gum,"},{"time":85839,"text":"Bazooka bubble gum\nwith the little cartoon wrappers inside,"},{"time":89932,"text":"Bazooka that we'd get\nonce a year in Ukraine"},{"time":93049,"text":"and we'd have to chew\none piece for an entire week."},{"time":97085,"text":"So the first day we get to New York,"},{"time":98891,"text":"my grandmother and I find a penny"},{"time":101124,"text":"in the floor of the homeless shelter\nthat my family's staying in."},{"time":104867,"text":"Only, we don't know\nthat it's a homeless shelter."},{"time":106402,"text":"We think that it's a hotel,\na hotel with lots of rats."},{"time":109493,"text":"So we find this penny kind\nof fossilized in the floor,"},{"time":114075,"text":"and we think that a very wealthy\nman must have left it there"},{"time":117071,"text":"because regular people\ndon't just lose money."},{"time":119565,"text":"And I hold this penny\nin the palm of my hand,"},{"time":122122,"text":"and it's sticky and rusty,"},{"time":124784,"text":"but it feels like I'm holding a fortune."},{"time":127815,"text":"I decide that I'm going\nto get my very own piece"},{"time":130125,"text":"of Bazooka bubble gum."},{"time":131940,"text":"And in that moment, I feel\nlike a millionaire."},{"time":135925,"text":"About a year later, I get\nto feel that way again"},{"time":138235,"text":"when we find a bag full\nof stuffed animals in the trash,"},{"time":140994,"text":"and suddenly I have more toys"},{"time":142725,"text":"than I've ever had in my whole life."},{"time":145469,"text":"And again, I get that feeling\nwhen we get a knock"},{"time":147854,"text":"on the door of our apartment in Brooklyn,"},{"time":149831,"text":"and my sister and I find a deliveryman"},{"time":152140,"text":"with a box of pizza that we didn't order."},{"time":154693,"text":"So we take the pizza,\nour very first pizza,"},{"time":157882,"text":"and we devour slice after slice"},{"time":160721,"text":"as the deliveryman stands there\nand stares at us from the doorway."},{"time":164110,"text":"And he tells us to pay,\nbut we don't speak English."},{"time":167110,"text":"My mother comes out,\nand he asks her for money,"},{"time":169538,"text":"but she doesn't have enough."},{"time":170896,"text":"She walks 50 blocks\nto and from work every day"},{"time":174248,"text":"just to avoid spending money on bus fare."},{"time":176917,"text":"Then our neighbor pops her head in,"},{"time":178783,"text":"and she turns red with rage\nwhen she realizes"},{"time":181373,"text":"that those immigrants from downstairs"},{"time":183719,"text":"have somehow gotten\ntheir hands on her pizza."},{"time":187728,"text":"Everyone's upset."},{"time":189284,"text":"But the pizza is delicious."},{"time":193125,"text":"It doesn't hit me until years\nlater just how little we had."},{"time":199086,"text":"On our 10 year anniversary\nof being in the U.S.,"},{"time":201400,"text":"we decided to celebrate\nby reserving a room"},{"time":203508,"text":"at the hotel that we first stayed\nin when we got to the U.S."},{"time":206390,"text":"The man at the front desk\nlaughs, and he says,"},{"time":208809,"text":"\"You can't reserve a room here.\nThis is a homeless shelter.\""},{"time":211691,"text":"And we were shocked."},{"time":213828,"text":"My husband Brian was also\nhomeless as a kid."},{"time":217834,"text":"His family lost everything, and at age 11,"},{"time":220924,"text":"he had to live in motels with his dad,"},{"time":223677,"text":"motels\nthat would round up all of their food"},{"time":226610,"text":"and keep it hostage until they were\nable to pay the bill."},{"time":230290,"text":"And one time, when he finally got his box"},{"time":232495,"text":"of Frosted Flakes back, it\nwas crawling with roaches."},{"time":236091,"text":"But he did have one thing."},{"time":238007,"text":"He had this shoebox that he carried\nwith him everywhere"},{"time":240651,"text":"containing nine comic books,"},{"time":243114,"text":"two G.I. Joes painted\nto look like Spider-Man"},{"time":246260,"text":"and five Gobots. And\nthis was his treasure."},{"time":249323,"text":"This was his own assembly of heroes"},{"time":252318,"text":"that kept him from drugs and gangs"},{"time":254521,"text":"and from giving up on his dreams."},{"time":257317,"text":"I'm going to tell you about one more"},{"time":258365,"text":"formerly homeless member of our family."},{"time":261156,"text":"This is Scarlett."},{"time":262855,"text":"Once upon a time, Scarlet\nwas used as bait in dog fights."},{"time":265924,"text":"She was tied up and thrown into the ring"},{"time":268340,"text":"for other dogs to attack so they'd get\nmore aggressive before the fight."},{"time":272376,"text":"And now, these days, she eats organic food"},{"time":276616,"text":"and she sleeps on an orthopedic\nbed with her name on it,"},{"time":279307,"text":"but when we pour water\nfor her in her bowl,"},{"time":283559,"text":"she still looks up and she wags\nher tail in gratitude."},{"time":287548,"text":"Sometimes Brian and I walk\nthrough the park with Scarlett,"},{"time":290766,"text":"and she rolls through the grass,"},{"time":293185,"text":"and we just look at her"},{"time":295586,"text":"and then we look at each other"},{"time":297406,"text":"and we feel gratitude."},{"time":301413,"text":"We forget about all of our new\nmiddle-class frustrations"},{"time":305044,"text":"and disappointments,"},{"time":306919,"text":"and we feel like millionaires."},{"time":309603,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":310753,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}